headline: The Hartford Insurance Group Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: The Hartford Insurance Group (NYSE:HIG) used its fourth-quarter 2025 earnings call to highlight what management described as an “outstanding” year of performance, supported by profitable growth across its underwriting businesses, higher investment income, and continued capital returns to shareholder
